responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "E795A7E94FDA9592E8566BBC42982DEA", "We\'re still piecing it together. They\'re automata, no doubt. Crafted, not born. But by who? And for what reason? Their resemblance to us is... unsettling. Some seem to be performing ancient tasks, like mining or smithing, but with no discernible output. Others just stand guard, or worse, attack anyone who isn\'t one of them.They weren\'t in any of our records of Mt. Dun.")
name: ANV_FTUE_Dunir_GatewatcherStonebeard_11_Response
